nodes.text: J'Kek M'hoy Trinia was the leader of a faction of political philosophers on Goroth Prime. During the Corellian/Aqualish war, J'Kek M'hoy Trinia was critical of then-Rel'Kan, J'Kek D'rith Kalama and his policy of playing the Corellians and Aqualish were too risky and demanded he withdraw all concessions.
